                        {
                            "lang": "en",
                            "value": "A vulnerability was found in Exiv2. It has been declared as critical. Affected by this vulnerability is the function QuickTimeVideo::decodeBlock of the file quicktimevideo.cpp of the component QuickTime Video Handler. The manipulation leads to buffer overflow. The attack can be launched remotely. The name of the patch is d3651fdbd352cbaf259f89abf7557da343339378. It is recommended to apply a patch to fix this issue. The identifier VDB-212497 was assigned to this vulnerability."
